Toggle Bars 0.4.0 (2017-02-16)

    * The plugin is now considered compatible with
      all versions of Geany beginning with 1.27.
    * When first enabled (or after upgrading from 0.3.0),
      the plugin now asks for confirmation to hide the menu bar.


Toggle Bars 0.3.0 (2016-07-21)

    * The status bar is now automatically shown whenever
      the progress bar is shown (and hidden afterwards),
      to provide visual indication for long-running operations.


Toggle Bars 0.2.1 (2016-07-03)

    * First release.
